___________________________________________________________________________________
| cmds       -     contains the application's executable commands.          
| net        -     contains the application's network related components.
| etc        -     contains configuration files widely used across the app.
| var        -     contains the application variables and templates.
|
|___________________________________________________________________________________
| NET  - network related functionalities.
|___________________________________________________________________________________
|    sdu   -   as in service data unit.
|    sapi  -   as in service api.
|    www   -   points to webserver related functionalities.
|    opera -   stores fs core operations.
